  "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/#content)\n\n# Industrial Coatings Services\n\n## **Wet Paint**Coating\n\nOur wet paint coatings are applied with precision and expertise, providing a seamless and durable finish to a variety of surfaces.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/wet-paint-coatings/)\n\n## **Complex**Coating\n\nWe offer extensive technical knowledge and adept handling of complex coating systems to meet all unique challenges.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/complex-coating/)\n\n## **Abrasive Media**Blasting\n\nWith rigorous [standards set by SSPC and NACE](https://popsindustrial.com/request-a-quote/standards-specifications-certifications/), our skilled professionals & specialized equipment ensure optimal coating adhesion.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/complex-coating/)\n\n## **Durable Powder**Coating\n\nElectrostatic spray process of dry powder cured for a tough, uniform surface with resistance to corrosion, impact and chemicals.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/powder-coating/)\n\n## **Large Capacity Powder**Coating\n\nUniquely tailored for large scale projects, we are skilled and equipped to take on both significant size and volume jobs.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/large-capacity-powder-coating/)\n\n## **Specifications &**Certifications\n\nPop’s Industrial Coatings is committed to quality work in full conformance with industry standards. See our certifications.\n\n[More](https://popsindustrial.com/request-a-quote/standards-specifications-certifications/)",
